{
  "stem": "18486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 273.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And through the organization, the person where she was [INAUDIBLE] got the other part.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when she came to a house of people she didn't know, she had her paper, and they fit it-- where it fitted together.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they knew they could trust each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For what reason?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when we had to bring-- oh, when they were caught?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when they were stopped, there was a good chance they were taken, of course, if they had not of-- a good story-- of a good--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that they-- that they didn't know anything about it, that they were going to a girlfriend, or whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of those things happened in a-- on bicycles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, first of all, in Holland, everybody goes on a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And secondly, we had no cars anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- but you were not too often stopped on the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you could fall in a trap, for instance, when-- when a house was invaded, and the Jews were taken, who were in the house-- they had found Jewish people there and they would-- had taken them-- then they also took the-- the people who lived in that house.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they left, usually, one of their soldiers, or men, in that empty house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when-- everybody who came to that house was taken.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you were always very careful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, we had a geranium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the geranium was standing in one window, always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When there was danger, that-- that-- the moment I saw German soldiers around the house, or in-- in the road, I took the geranium and put it in another window.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That meant for all our members, don't come to the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so when we were taken, we were absolutely sure that that thing was there.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
